-- Germans Reject Aid for Spain, ARD Television Says, Citing Poll
-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n
-- 2012-07-20T08:01:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-20/germans-reject-aid-for-spain-ard-television-says-citing-poll.html
Fifty-two percent of Germans are
against  Spain  receiving aid from the euro region financial
backstops, while 38 percent approve of the planned rescue, ARD
public television  said  on its Internet site, citing a poll it
commissioned from Infratest dimap.  ARD said Infratest interviewed 1,000 people between July 17
and July 18. The margin of error was 3.1 percentage points, it
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rainer Buergin in Berlin at 
